### Backend API Testing
### Base URL: http://localhost:5000

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:5000/api/health

###

### Authentication - Login
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@chandanportfolio.com",
  "password": "admin123456"
}

###

### Authentication - Get Profile (requires token)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Contact Form - Submit
POST http://localhost:5000/api/contact
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "subject": "Test Contact",
  "message": "This is a test message from the contact form."
}

###

### Contact - Get All (Admin only)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/contact
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Blog - Get All Blogs
GET http://localhost:5000/api/blog

###

### Blog - Get All Blogs with Pagination
GET http://localhost:5000/api/blog?page=1&limit=5&sort=-createdAt

###

### Blog - Search Blogs
GET http://localhost:5000/api/blog?search=javascript&category=technology

###

### Blog - Create Blog (Admin only)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/blog
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "title": "Getting Started with Node.js",
  "content": "Node.js is a powerful JavaScript runtime built on Chrome's V8 JavaScript engine. In this comprehensive guide, we'll explore how to get started with Node.js development...",
  "excerpt": "Learn the basics of Node.js development in this beginner-friendly guide.",
  "category": "technology",
  "tags": ["nodejs", "javascript", "backend", "tutorial"],
  "status": "published",
  "seoTitle": "Getting Started with Node.js - Complete Guide",
  "seoDescription": "Learn Node.js from scratch with this comprehensive guide covering installation, basics, and best practices.",
  "seoKeywords": ["nodejs", "javascript", "backend development", "tutorial"]
}

###

### Blog - Get Single Blog by ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/blog/BLOG_ID_HERE

###

### Blog - Get Single Blog by Slug
GET http://localhost:5000/api/blog/slug/getting-started-with-nodejs

###

### Blog - Update Blog (Admin only)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/blog/BLOG_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "title": "Getting Started with Node.js - Updated",
  "content": "Updated content here...",
  "status": "published"
}

###

### Blog - Delete Blog (Admin only)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/blog/BLOG_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Blog - Like Blog
POST http://localhost:5000/api/blog/BLOG_ID_HERE/like

###

### Blog - Get Related Blogs
GET http://localhost:5000/api/blog/BLOG_ID_HERE/related

###

### Users - Get All Users (Admin only)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/auth/users
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Users - Create User (Admin only)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "testpassword123",
  "role": "user",
  "bio": "Test user for API testing"
}

###

### Change Password
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/auth/change-password
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "currentPassword": "admin123456",
  "newPassword": "newpassword123"
}

###

### Contact Statistics (Admin only)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/contact/stats/overview
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

